{"tid":2340650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以悲劇收場？郭文貴語出驚人：馬雲會死無葬身之地","createTime":"2020-12-25T16:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T01:06:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1d417a1805ed9de9f9835ac4679143df0966c8","tid":2340650,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"2019/09/10 <br />\n<br />\n中國電商巨擘阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲今日正式卸任董事局主席一職，由於近年來中國「國進民退」，外界一直有馬雲「被退休」的說法。曾在去年宣稱馬雲就是江澤民家族白手套、被中國國家副主席王岐山威脅交出阿里巴巴控制權的中國反共富豪郭文貴美東時間9日直播時大膽預言，由於馬雲給太多中共高官許過諾，退休後的馬雲仍將「死無葬身之地」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2911446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2911446&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=11b31c14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2911446&h=dc660b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2911446</a>"},{"pid":"7b15f068ce0c5b92685463e3fbc68e808cccd48b","tid":2340650,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"姐係唔死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7daaac251ea04ffbadeb9c9d5b77643f6bbb0698","tid":2340650,"uid":68730,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"瞓咗冇睇 范冰冰啲相出咗未？"},{"pid":"f2c8bb01626c89133ddb44225c58abf36e9a52dc","tid":2340650,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"條𡃁係香港俾人斬都冇左件事啦"},{"pid":"ac9728e3ad1900c88674111274e2765f37d241c4","tid":2340650,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318d495f59a8e7e23c7087b1212702953f196f0c","tid":2340650,"uid":20170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:09:59.000Z","msg":